-- Ryanair Reports First-Half Adjusted Profit $632 Million, Raises Forecast
-- B y   S t e v e   R o t h w e l l
-- 2010-11-01T06:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/ryanair-reports-first-half-adjusted-profit-632-million-raises-forecast.html
Ryanair Holdings Plc  said its first
half adjusted profit after tax, excluding exceptional items, was
451.9 million euros, compared with 387 million euros in the year
earlier period.  The company raised its forecast for full year net profit to
within a range of 380 million euros to 400 million euros,
according to a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Steve Rothwell  in London at 
